mtcars |>
  ggplot(aes(wt, mpg)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = lm) +
  stat_smooth(method = lm, 
              geom = 'point',
              xseq = c(2,3), 
              size = 3, 
              color = "blue") +
  stat_smooth(method = lm,
              geom = "segment", # draw fitted values as points
              color = "darkred",
              xseq = c(2,3), # 'from', 'to' value pair
              aes(yend = after_stat(y[1]), # 'from' value of y
                  xend = 3), # 'to' value of x
              arrow = arrow(ends = c("last", "first"), 
                            length = unit(.1, "in")))

std <- function(x){
  
  (x - mean(x))/sd(x)
  
}

mtcars |>
  ggplot() +
  aes(std(wt), std(mpg)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = lm) +
  stat_smooth(method = lm, 
              geom = 'point',
              xseq = c(0,1), 
              size = 3, 
              color = "blue") +
  stat_smooth(method = lm,
              geom = "segment", # draw fitted values as points
              color = "darkred",
              xseq = c(0,1), # 'from', 'to' value pair
              aes(yend = after_stat(y[1]), # 'from' value of y
                  xend = 1), # 'to' value of x
              arrow = arrow(ends = c("last", "first"), 
                            length = unit(.1, "in"))) + 
  coord_fixed() + 
  annotate(geom = "point",
           x = 0, y = 0,
           shape = 4,
           size = 200,
           alpha = .3)
